 Isa Rambo, Area Commander, Suleja Area Command of the Nigeria Police Force, who was kidnapped in Kaduna has been rescued.Rambo, an Assistant Commissioner of Police, was kidnapped on his way to Jos, Plateau State, on Saturday.The kidnappers demanded a ransom of N50 million before releasing him.



